# .semgrepignore
# Files and paths excluded from Semgrep SAST scanning.
# Semgrep respects .semgrepignore the same way git respects .gitignore.

# Terraform provider cache
.terraform/
**/.terraform/

# Terraform state files — contain sensitive data, not source code
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup

# Lock files — dependency manifests, not application logic
*.lock.hcl
*.lock

# Git internals
.git/
